drigo-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-2023-3530414">于 11 月</a>Crow 入选摇滚名人堂时再次合作表演。</p><p>在其他地方，下一次“Guts”世界巡演将于今晚（3 月 13 日）在内布拉斯加州奥马哈 CHI 健康中心拉开帷幕。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-2024-guts-world-tour-shows-buy-tickets-3497458">请访问此处查看完整的日期列表</a>，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Folivia-rodrigo-tickets%2Fartist%2F2836194" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-handing-out-free-plan-b-and-condoms-on-tour-funding-abortion-its-a-good-idea-right-3600739">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 在巡演中免费发放 Plan B 和安全套的帖子：“资助堕胎？这是个好主意，对吧？”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
